

              neovim-fuzzy


Provides fuzzy file finding for neovim, via fzy[1].

[1]: https://github.com/jhawthorn/fzy

. Dependencies

  * fzy

. Installation

  Install `fzy` via your package manager, or check https://github.com/jhawthorn/fzy
  for instructions.

  If you're using vim-plug, add this to your vimrc:

      Plug 'cloudhead/neovim-fuzzy'

. Usage

  Hit <Ctrl-P> to open the finder. Hit <Enter> to jump to the selected file
  and <Esc> to close the pane.

